@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/PrivacyPolicy.css" />
<div class="privacy-policy">
	<article class="privacy-policy-rules">
    <h3 class="privacy-policy-title">YumYum Now - Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p class="privacy-policy-last-upd">Last Updated: 23.11.2023</p>
    
    <p class="privacy-policy-greetings">
        Welcome to YumYum Now! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our food delivery service specializing in street food.
    </p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">1. Information We Collect</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">1.1 Account Information: When you create an account on YumYum Now, we collect information such as your name, email address, and password.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">1.2 Order Information: When you place an order through YumYum Now, we collect details such as your delivery address, order preferences, and payment information.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">1.3 Device Information: We may collect information about the device you use to access YumYum Now, including the device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">1.4 Location Information: With your consent, we may collect your location information to provide accurate delivery services.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">2. How We Use Your Information</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">2.1 Order Fulfillment: We use the information you provide to process and fulfill your street food orders.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">2.2 Account Management: Your account information is used to manage your YumYum Now account and provide personalized services.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">2.3 Communication: We may use your email address to send order confirmations, updates, and promotional offers. You can opt-out of promotional emails at any time.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">2.4 Improving Services: We analyze user data to enhance our platform, services, and user experience.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">3. Information Sharing</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">3.1 Vendors: We share necessary information with street food vendors to fulfill your orders.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">3.2 Service Providers: We may share information with third-party service providers that assist us in delivering our services, such as payment processors and delivery partners.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">3.3 Legal Compliance: We may disclose information when required by law or in response to legal requests.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">4. Security</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">4.1 We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">4.2 While we take reasonable steps to safeguard your information, no online platform can guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">5. Your Choices</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">5.1 You can manage your communication preferences by adjusting your account settings or contacting customer support.</p>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">5.2 You may disable location services, but this may affect the accuracy of our delivery services.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">6. Children's Privacy</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">6.1 YumYum Now is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under 13 years of age.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">7. Changes to Privacy Policy</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">7.1 YumYum Now reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy. Users will be notified of any changes, and continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <h5 class="privacy-policy-rule-name">8. Contact Us</h5>
    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">8.1 If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact our privacy team at YumYumNow@hotmail.com.</p>

    <p class="privacy-policy-rule">
        Thank you for choosing YumYum Now! We appreciate your trust in us to deliver delicious street food to your doorstep.
    </p>
</article>

</div>
